{"tid":2411242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"常用作文題目100題","createTime":"2021-02-17T07:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T08:46:40.000Z","uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0c91e9fcbfbd6a333166c769555c8d9a043125","tid":2411242,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.shareclass.org/course/5494c9086f28488ca28789e02bff2688/material/c3b7db6c36df492db3ed9cc4bb43d320/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shareclass.org%2Fcourse%2F5494c9086f28488ca28789e02bff2688%2Fmaterial%2Fc3b7db6c36df492db3ed9cc4bb43d320%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=41d36d03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shareclass.org/course/5494c9086f28488ca28789e02bff2688/material/c3b7db6c36df492db3ed9cc4bb43d320/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZpd8TL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZpd8TL.jpg&h=4ee18be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OV8XM5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OV8XM5.jpg&h=958bd504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8PaEj0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8PaEj0q.jpg&h=585d8984&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6242d906b8d815334c7557f62da540559cb66ec","tid":2411242,"uid":76885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:09:38.000Z","msg":"《開學了》<br />\n<br />\n要開學了。過了長假，身心都慢了下來。長假中，我漫無目的地四處遊玩著。在山林間，看看樹、看看花、聽聽蟲叫，也聽聽風吹。在書籍間，乘著作者的字詞，在其思想軌道亂穿亂插。誰知，分不清甚麼是現實、甚麼是白日夢時，假日的限期就將我領回到扎扎實實的現實。<br />\n<br />\n要開學了。上學時，我要做個稱職的好同學，在同學叫喚時，我要做些討人喜歡的回應，讓對方感覺到我虛構的血肉。上課時，老師講學時，我要看著她們，也要點點頭，讓她們自覺所說的話起碼進了那個誰的耳朵，算是送她們一些安慰或存在感。<br />\n<br />\n要開學了。又要進入人類社會的群體了；又要裝裝做個正常人了；又要費勁完成些社交儀式了。或者其實我心底在長假中一直寂寞著，或者我對這天也期待已久了吧。<br />\n<br />\n（303字）"},{"pid":"a92f6d905d46a87626b8cd972aa06c715585fea3","tid":2411242,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"當初原意 想自我教育 想由小學既語文要求開始 訓練下自己既語文能力 <br />\n所以就搵小學作文題材 試下做 就下搵返書面語既感覺 試下練唔練到文筆 <br />\n<br />\n一年前就想做下類似既野 算係拖延左一年<br />\n<blockquote>有無人覺得自己文筆好差，想進步？其實要點做？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510871\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510871</a><br />\n<br />\n寫既時候 感覺無病呻吟 感覺無想寫或必要寫既野<br />\n<br />\n記得細個作文 好似會起稿 好似會大致plan下結構 plan下每節內容同幾長<br />\n而家寫 就好似將相對空廢既內容 隨意咁寫出<br />\n<br />\n唔計內容 計文字 可能都好多語病？<br />\n可能就由作文作為起點 都自學下中文語法 去令自己可以俾自己反饋？<br />\n不過呢樣野要做 可能又再要拖延好長好長"},{"pid":"4156efd7d4671fc093cfc5d0f80796c550c6a4e7","tid":2411242,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://blog.amazingtalker.com/zh-tw/zh-eng/國高中必背8000單字表/3747/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.amazingtalker.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fzh-eng%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%85%E8%83%8C8000%E5%96%AE%E5%AD%97%E8%A1%A8%2F3747%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=d857303e\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.amazingtalker.com/zh-tw/zh-eng/國高中必背8000單字表/3747/</a><br />\n<br />\n我英文都好差<br />\n如果每日學下十個生字<br />\n<br />\nblanket <br />\nabroad<br />\nbake<br />\nbakery<br />\nbalcony = an area with a wall or bars around it that is joined to the outside wall of a building on an upper level<br />\n<br />\ncentimeter<br />\nchalk<br />\nbowl<br />\nchopsticks<br />\napartment = a set of rooms for living in, especially on one floor of a building"},{"pid":"594064b73a38f999bad037d1cd6488c6b80dc476","tid":2411242,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mathsisfun.com/algebra/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mathsisfun.com%2Falgebra%2Findex.html&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=63f48f6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mathsisfun.com/algebra/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n數學都好差"}]}